products.name: Bank of China Great Wall International MasterCard Credit Card (Low Fee Card)
products.description:
The Bank of China Great Wall International Credit Card (Credit Card) can be used for making purchases and at any ATM in Australia and overseas displaying a MasterCard logo or for cash withdrawals at any Bank of China retail branches in Australia. You will enjoy up to 55 days of Interest-free period on purchases.
 
The Credit Card also provides you with other features such as Smart Interest Free Instalment Plan and maximum Monthly Usage Limit for additional cardholders.
